    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This spell lets you convince an animal that you mean it no harm. Choose a Beast or creature with the Animal tag that you can see within range. It must see and hear you. If the creature’s INT is 4 (−3) or higher, the spell fails. Otherwise, the creature must succeed on a WIS save or be charmed by you for the spell’s duration. If you or one of your companions harms the target, the spell ends.</p><p><em>At Higher Circles.</em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd circle or higher, you can affect one additional creature for each slot above 1st.</p>",
